metadata.title: JED - Juvenile and Escapement Data

creators.name: Oceans Canada, Science Branch - Data Analyst

metadata.description:
Parameter
Biological data sampled from adult and jack hatchery reared salmonids

Measurement Details
Data include eggs taken, sold and transferred, juveniles ponded sold, transferred and released, releases stored by mark, Coded Wire Tag (CWT) and release site, adult sampling records, and estimates of spawning escapements.

Geographic Area
Coastal British Columbia production areas

Other Comments
Escapement data has only been entered for the past five years.

[ A TCODE project ]
